1. What is Repository Pattern in Laravel?
Answer: Repository pattern ek design pattern hai jo business logic aur database queries ko alag karta hai.
Explanation: Jaise kitchen aur living room alag hote hain, waise hi Repository business aur database ka kaam alag karta hai.

2. What is Laravel Contract?
Answer: Contracts Laravel mein ek set of rules hote hain jo batate hain ki koi service kaise kaam karegi.
Explanation: Jaise school mein rules hote hain ki sabko uniform pehna hai, waise hi Contracts set karte hain ki code kaise behave karega.

3. What are Policies in Laravel?
Answer: Policies authorization ke rules define karte hain ki user kya kar sakta hai ya nahi.
Explanation: Jaise guard decide karta hai ki kaun office mein andar ja sakta hai, waise Policies decide karti hain user ke rights.

4. What is Laravel Observer?
Answer: Observer ek class hoti hai jo automatically kuch kaam karti hai jab database mein kuch change hota hai.
Explanation: Jaise camera automatically motion detect karta hai, waise Observer database changes ko observe karta hai.

5. What is Laravel Broadcast Driver?
Answer: Broadcast driver real-time updates bhejne ke liye use hota hai, jaise Pusher, Redis, etc.
Explanation: Jaise TV ka signal alag drivers (dish, cable) se aata hai, waise hi broadcast drivers use hote hain.

6. What is Laravel Notification System?
Answer: Notification system se hum emails, SMS, ya database notifications bhej sakte hain.
Explanation: Jaise mobile mein message ya notification pop aata hai, waise Laravel notifications send karta hai.

7. What is Laravel Horizon?
Answer: Horizon ek dashboard hai jo queues aur jobs ko monitor karta hai.
Explanation: Jaise hospital mein ek screen hoti hai jisme patients ka status dikhata hai, waise Horizon queues ka status dikhata hai.

8. What is Rate Limiting in Laravel?
Answer: Rate limiting ek system hai jo ek user kitni requests bhej sakta hai, usko control karta hai.
Explanation: Jaise ek restaurant mein ek time mein sirf ek order lete hain, waise hi rate limit request control karta hai.

9. What is Lazy Loading and Eager Loading in Laravel?
Answer: Lazy loading mein jab zarurat hoti hai tab data load hota hai, eager loading mein pehle se load kar lete hain.
Explanation: Jaise tum ghar se bahar jaane se pehle pura bag ready karte ho (eager) ya zarurat padne par saman lete ho (lazy).

10. What is Throttling in Laravel?
Answer: Throttling request ko limit karne ka ek aur method hai, jisse server overload nahi hota.
Explanation: Jaise ek ek karke log lift mein jaate hain, waise throttling request control karta hai.

11. What is Laravel Passport?
Answer: Passport ek package hai jo secure API authentication ke liye OAuth2 system use karta hai.
Explanation: Jaise airport pehchaan ke liye passport dikhana padta hai, waise API users apna passport token dikhate hain.

12. What is Laravel Socialite?
Answer: Socialite se login systems jaise Google, Facebook ka easy integration hota hai.
Explanation: Jaise kisi party mein special pass se bina rukawat entry milti hai, waise hi Socialite login ko asaan banata hai.

13. What is Laravel Macro?
Answer: Macro se hum Laravel ke core classes mein naye functions add kar sakte hain.
Explanation: Jaise tum apne mobile mein naye apps install karte ho, waise hi Macro se naye features add hote hain.

14. What is Laravel Scout?
Answer: Scout ek search package hai jo fast aur full-text search provide karta hai.
Explanation: Jaise tum Google mein type karte hi suggestions milte hain, waise Scout fast search results deta hai.

15. How to Schedule a Task in Laravel?
Answer: Hum schedule() function use karke task schedule kar sakte hain, aur cron job set karte hain.
Explanation: Jaise alarm set karte ho subah uthne ke liye, waise schedule tasks set karte hain automatic kaam ke liye.

16. What is Laravel Event Broadcasting with Pusher?
Answer: Broadcasting with Pusher real-time messages send karne ke liye hota hai jaise chat apps mein hota hai.
Explanation: Jaise WhatsApp mein message send karte hi dusre bande ko turant milta hai, waise Broadcasting work karta hai.

17. What is Laravel Mix?
Answer: Laravel Mix ek tool hai jo CSS, JS ko compile aur optimize karta hai.
Explanation: Jaise ek washing machine kapdon ko clean aur ready karti hai, waise hi Mix front-end files ko ready karta hai.

18. What is Inertia.js in Laravel?
Answer: Inertia.js Laravel aur Vue/React apps ko bina API banaye direct connect karta hai.
Explanation: Jaise direct phone call karne se jaldi baat hoti hai, waise Inertia.js se server aur front-end fast connect hote hain.

19. What is Laravel Fortify?
Answer: Fortify authentication ke liye ek backend package hai jaise login, register, reset password ke features deta hai.
Explanation: Jaise ek strong lock ghar ko secure karta hai, waise Fortify app ke login ko secure karta hai.

20. What is Laravel Jetstream?
Answer: Jetstream ek full starter kit hai authentication, team management aur profile ke saath.
Explanation: Jaise ek poora furnished flat milta hai ready-to-live, waise Jetstream ready-to-use authentication deta hai.

21. What is Laravel Breeze?
Answer: Breeze ek simple aur light authentication starter kit hai Laravel ke liye.
Explanation: Jaise ek chhoti lightweight bike tez chalti hai, waise Breeze chhota aur simple hai Jetstream ke comparison mein.

22. What is Laravel Livewire?
Answer: Livewire se hum PHP se hi front-end interactivity kar sakte hain bina JavaScript ke.
Explanation: Jaise remote control se bina wire ke TV chala sakte ho, waise Livewire PHP se front-end handle karta hai.

23. What is Database Transactions in Laravel?
Answer: Transaction ek group of queries ko ek saath successfully complete karne ka system hai.
Explanation: Jaise bank mein paisa transfer tabhi hota hai jab dono account ka process successful ho, waise hi transaction kaam karta hai.

24. What is Laravel Task Scheduling Frequency Options?
Answer: Hum tasks ko hourly, daily, weekly, ya custom frequency se run karwa sakte hain.
Explanation: Jaise tum alarm ko daily ya weekly set karte ho, waise tasks ko timing se set kar sakte ho.

25. What is Laravel Testing (Feature & Unit Test)?
Answer: Feature test pura system check karta hai, Unit test chhoti chhoti cheeze check karta hai.
Explanation: Jaise car ka pura test hota hai (feature) aur sirf tyre ka test hota hai (unit).

26. What is Laravel Service Container?
Answer: Service container ek system hai jo classes ko banata hai aur dependencies ko inject karta hai.
Explanation: Jaise ek storeroom mein saman ready rehta hai use karne ke liye, waise hi service container dependencies ready rakhta hai.

27. What is Laravel Service Binding?
Answer: Service binding se hum batate hain ki service container mein kaunsi class use karni hai.
Explanation: Jaise tum decide karte ho ki TV remote kaunsa lena hai, waise binding batata hai kaunsa service use karni hai.

28. What is Laravel Custom Validation Rule?
Answer: Custom validation se hum apne khud ke validation logic bana sakte hain.
Explanation: Jaise apne ghar ke rule alag bana sakte ho jaise "shoes allowed nahi," waise custom validation bana sakte ho.

29. What is Laravel Events Service Provider?
Answer: EventServiceProvider event aur listener ko register karne ka place hota hai.
Explanation: Jaise school ka timetable principal ke office mein ready hota hai, waise events EventServiceProvider mein ready hote hain.

30. What is Laravel UUID?
Answer: UUID ek unique ID hoti hai jo randomly generate hoti hai, database mein ID ke jagah use hoti hai.
Explanation: Jaise tumhara Aadhaar number unique hota hai, waise UUID har record ke liye unique hota hai.
